<para>Specify which EOC (End Of Conversion) flag is used for conversion by polling and interruption: end of unitary conversion or end of sequence conversions. This parameter can be a value of <ref refid="group__ADC__EOCSelection" kindref="compound">ADC sequencer end of unitary conversion or sequence conversions</ref>. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
        <location file="/home/runner/work/cubesat/cubesat/eps/v1/firmware/bootstrap/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_hal_adc.h" line="127" column="12" bodyfile="/home/runner/work/cubesat/cubesat/eps/v1/firmware/bootstrap/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_hal_adc.h" bodystart="127" bodyend="-1"/>
